# Committed listing-cache snapshots + their integrity sidecars live here.
#
# The repo-root .gitignore ignores *.sqlite3 everywhere. Re-include this directory's
# snapshot files (only <=20MB should actually be committed — a larger snapshot must be
# excluded manually) and ALWAYS re-include the .sha256 / .meta.json sidecars so a
# committed benchmark package can be integrity-checked from the tree alone.
!*.sqlite3
!*.sha256
!*.meta.json
!.gitignore
